----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Test case name:  TC_L30SW_Q-36684436: Testcase_to_verify_the_functionality_of_interface_DsblHWIO_GM_TaskInits_to_prohibits_all_application_defined_RTOS_tasks_and_application_ISRs_from_pre_empting_the_current_task_or_ISR_on_the_CPU3.
